# 3DSendai C style (AGENTS.md): 2-space indent, spaces not tabs, 100 cols.
# Reuses 3Drop's clang-format shape; indent adapted to this repo's convention.
BasedOnStyle: LLVM
IndentWidth: 2
TabWidth: 2
UseTab: Never
ColumnLimit: 100
AllowShortFunctionsOnASingleLine: Empty
AllowShortIfStatementsOnASingleLine: WithoutElse
AllowShortLoopsOnASingleLine: false
AlignAfterOpenBracket: Align
SortIncludes: false
